BT 1 0 0 1 0 55.2 Tm /F1 9.3 Tf 12.9 TL 1.69238 Tw (Northstar is built as a React frontend consuming a dedicated analytics microservice backed by a ClickHouse) Tj T* 0 Tw .664714 Tw (analytical database. Event data flows from the main Vantage Loop application through the event pipeline into ClickHouse) Tj T* 0 Tw .152982 Tw (via a Kafka ingestion pipeline. The analytics service exposes a REST API; all dashboard queries are cacheable at) Tj T* 0 Tw .94945 Tw (the service layer with a 5-minute TTL. Exports are handled by a separate async worker pool to prevent latency) Tj T* 0 Tw (impact on the interactive dashboard.) Tj T* ET
Q
Q
q
1 0 0 1 70.8 561.8 cm
Q
q
1 0 0 1 70.8 510.2 cm
q
.164706 .14902 .133333 rg
BT 1 0 0 1 0 42.3 Tm /F1 9.3 Tf 12.9 TL .597808 Tw (Authentication uses the identity provider SSO; authorization is role-based within each enterprise account. The shared-link token) Tj T* 0 Tw .791305 Tw (\(NS-F003\) uses a signed JWT stored in the analytics service; it does not grant the identity provider session access. All data in) Tj T* 0 Tw .883306 Tw (transit is TLS 1.3. Data at rest in ClickHouse is encrypted using AES-256. The deployment runs on the container platform) Tj T* 0 Tw (\(EKS\); the monitoring platform monitors latency and error rates; the error-tracking tool captures frontend and backend exceptions.) Tj T* ET
Q
Q
